.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=5cc1co3unir7jujspt8uvvkh86&q1=Jeannie+Seely&q2=Country+Singles&interval=20|magazine=[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]]|accessdate=24 April 2012|date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402142234/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=5cc1co3unir7jujspt8uvvkh86&q1=Jeannie+Seely&q2=Country+Singles&interval=20|archive-date=2 April 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"If I Can't Have You\"<ref name=\"whitburn\">{{cite book|last=Whitburn|first=Joel|title=Hot Country Songs 1944 to 2008|publisher=Record Research, Inc.|year=2008|isbn=0-89820-177-2}}</ref>\n| 1964\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| {{n/a}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Bring It on Back\"<ref name=\"whitburn\"/>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 1965\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| {{n/a}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Today Is Not the Day\"<ref name=\"whitburn\"/>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| {{n/a}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Don't Touch Me]]\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1966\n| 85 || 2 || 29 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''The Seely Style''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[It's Only Love (Jeannie Seely song)|It's Only Love]]\"\n| \u2014 || 15 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[A Wanderin' Man]]\"\n| \u2014 || 13 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Thanks, Hank!''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"When It's Over\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1967\n| \u2014 || 39 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''I'll Love You More''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"These Memories\"\n| \u2014 || 42 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Thanks, Hank!''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[I'll Love You More (Than You'll Need)]]\"\n| \u2014 || 10 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''I'll Love You More''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Welcome Home to Nothing\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1968\n| \u2014 || 24 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''Little Things''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"How Is He\"\n| \u2014 || 23 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Little Things\"<ref name=\"whitburn\"/>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Just En